ARTICLE.TITLE: Final Year Exam 2020: Lucknow University releases exam datesheet on lkouniv.ac.in- check schedule here
ARTICLE.TEXT:
Lucknow University releases exam datesheet on lkouniv.ac.in | Photo Credit: Representative Image

Lucknow University has released the Final Year Exam 2020 date sheet on August 12, 2020. The time table is available on the official site of Lucknow University at lkouniv.ac.in. The examination would begin on September 8 and would end on September 19, 2020. The time table has been released for BA, BSc, BCom, and other undergraduate level programmes.

The official notice of the exam time table is the available college wise. Students who will apply for the examination can check the complete schedule below.

Final Year Exam 2020: Complete Schedule

BA Final Year Exam 2020 September 7 to September 18, 2020 BSc Home Science Final Year Exam 2020 September 7 to September 12, 2020 BCom Final Year Exam 2020 September 7 to September 19, 2020

Lucknow University this time has decided to conduct the final year exams through the Multiple Choice Format question paper. To help familiarize students with the new format of question paper which will be used for Lucknow University Final Year Exams 2020, the varsity has also released dedicated subject-wise sample papers.

With the help of these sample papers, students can check out the MCQ format and also know how to answer the question. The question paper will have four answers to each question. For more related details candidates can visit the official site of Lucknow University.
